JOIN UNITED'S 1221 CLUB AND
DO YOUR FLYING AT ½ PRICE!
If you're over 12 and under 22, United's 1221 Club wants
you! It's United's special fare advantage that lets you fly
with us for half the price of a regular jet coach ticket.*
You can't reserve a seat, but you can fly at half fare when
space is
available and after military standbys have
boarded.
A glance at the map above will show you United's plan is
the one to join. With more flights to more U.S. cities than
any other airline, you can see the opportunities the 1221
Club offers you in the friendly skies of United.
United's 1221 Club is easy to join. Go to any United
Ticket Office or United Ticket Counter at the airport. Give
the man $3.00 and
proof of age. Your 1221 membership
card will be mailed to you.
*Good only for travel on United Air Lines in the continental United
States, except intra state travel. Not applicable 4/7, 11/23, 11/27,
and 12/15 to 12/24 inclusive.
